Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.78,0:24:14.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}务必觅得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:19.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}微眠之约
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:40.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}萌生此等惬意  实乃徒增彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:51.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:57.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未萦他意
